Package: chatops-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: ChatOps Team <support@chatops.com>
Description: ChatOps Agent - Server monitoring and management agent
 ChatOps Agent is a lightweight agent that runs on servers to collect
 metrics, manage Docker containers, and execute commands remotely.
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce
Recommends: systemd

